  "texts": [
    "Results How Germans assess GenAI as a source of science-related contentOverall, as of August 2023, Germans were cautious when assessing GenAI as a source of science-related content.",
    "On the one hand, when asked to evaluate the possibilities of \"programs like ChatGPT\" in science communication, half of the respondents (53%) \"agreed\" or \"completely agreed\" that the ability to explain complex scientific content in a highly simplified way is positive about GenAI (see Figure 2).",
    "Similarly, 50% of respondents stated that the capability of GenAI to provide examples and answer questions when there are uncertainties about scientific subjects is positive.",
    "Between 23% and 29%, however, did not rate these aspects positively.",
    "On the other hand, only one-third of respondents viewed GenAI's ability to engage users in science-related conversations akin to human interaction and generating texts in the style of scientific papers in a very short time as something positive."
  ],
  "correct_citations": []
}